languages.text: "Но нам повезло! Мы живы и справляемся — нас зараза не берет!"
"We got lucky, though! We're alive, we're getting by — the disease couldn't claim us!"
languages.original_text: "Но нам повезло! Мы живы и справляемся — нас зараза не берет!"

languages.text: “不过，我们很幸运！我们还活着，还在喘气！疾病别想要我们的命！”
languages.original_text: "We got lucky, though! We're alive, we're getting by — the disease couldn't claim us!"

traits.locale_text: “不过，我们很幸运！我们还活着，还在喘气！疾病别想要我们的命！”

languages.text: «¡Pero hemos tenido suerte! Seguimos vivos y aguantando... ¡la enfermedad no nos ha afectado!».
languages.original_text: "We got lucky, though! We're alive, we're getting by — the disease couldn't claim us!"

traits.locale_text: «¡Pero hemos tenido suerte! Seguimos vivos y aguantando... ¡la enfermedad no nos ha afectado!».

languages.text: 「だけど私達は幸運でした！生き延びてなんとかやり過ごせた…病気に命を奪われずに済みました！」
languages.original_text: "We got lucky, though! We're alive, we're getting by — the disease couldn't claim us!"

traits.locale_text: 「だけど私達は幸運でした！生き延びてなんとかやり過ごせた…病気に命を奪われずに済みました！」

languages.text: "Wir hatten Glück! Wir leben noch, wir halten durch – die Krankheit hat uns nicht erwischt!"
languages.original_text: "We got lucky, though! We're alive, we're getting by — the disease couldn't claim us!"

traits.locale_text: "Wir hatten Glück! Wir leben noch, wir halten durch – die Krankheit hat uns nicht erwischt!"

languages.text: « Mais nous, on a eu de la chance ! On est en vie, on s'en sort... La maladie nous a épargnés ! »
languages.original_text: "We got lucky, though! We're alive, we're getting by — the disease couldn't claim us!"

traits.locale_text: « Mais nous, on a eu de la chance ! On est en vie, on s'en sort... La maladie nous a épargnés ! »

languages.text: "Yine de şanslıyız! Yaşıyoruz, idare ediyoruz. Hastalık bize musallat olamadı!"
